    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether completing a computer-based program alters
      changes how the brain processes emotional information and improves symptoms of depression.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
